title: Shaghun
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian restaurant. Menu includes many vegetarians and some vegan dishes, and staff is willing to change any dish to meet the customers needs. Ayurvedic, veg, macrobiotic. Relaxed atmosphere. Has Wi-Fi, a lending library, Indian wine and beer. English spoken.
